eople...</span><hr size=1> To be honest, this is a game, and it has been consistently shown and continuously documented that this game is full of retards.  On the other hand, you did pick that name, and it does have real world connotations, both positive and negative.  A lot of people don't put a lot of thought into their names which is why we have so many players in this game with silly to downright stupid names, and it does reflect back upon them. <br>
<br>
Obviously, this is just a stupid game, and while I personally wouldn't name myself Nighthawk or Krusher or something along that line, I don't judge people on their names.  But, some people do.  My current character's name is a derivative of my original character's name, which I chose from a Roman Emperor.  My name choice had little significance.  I needed a name, and I couldn't think of anything good, so I busted out the encyclopedia.  I've gotten various tells in the past of people asking me about my name, and as an end result, I've learned quite a bit about said Emperor.  I changed the name slightly for this Bard, so I get less now.  <br>
<br>
You opted for a less than fantasy sounding name, and, as such, have to signed on for any commentary or discussion, good or bad &lt;shrug&gt;.  I learned this a long time ago, and as such, decided that even a nonsensical, yet fantasy sounding name works for me to avoid the roving bands of rabid morons that prowl in these games.  Names are a bigger deal than most people think, because, in a game of cookie cutter, dress up doll characters like Everquest, your name is your first impression on most people.<br>
<br>
Never the less, I grouped with you a few times, and you are definately a good player, and it obviously made at least a simple impact upon me because I went out of my way to help you get to Sebilis a couple weeks back.  <br>
<br>
Hadrien<br>
Smart Ass Bard of Saryrn <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showMessage?topicID=798.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.showMessage?topicID=803.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.emailToFriend?topicID=768.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.threadControl?topicID=768.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/grunge/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=768.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub12.ezboard.com/fthesaryrntavernthefurnace.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=768.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub12.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesaryrntaverncommonsroom">Commons Room<option value="thesaryrntavernfrm12">Screens -n- Things<option value="thesaryrntavernthesaryrnmarketplace">The Saryrn Marketplace<option value="thesaryrntavernclassdiscussion">Class Discussion<option value="thesaryrntavernfrm9">Class Epic Quests<option value="thesaryrntavernthefurnace">The Blast Furnace<option value="thesaryrntavernmmorpgtherisforroleplaying">MMORPG: The R is fo